  <sys:String x:Key="CharacterPickerColPick">選擇</sys:String>
  <sys:String x:Key="EditPanelPickCharacter">選擇角色…</sys:String>
  <sys:String x:Key="EditPanelPickCharacterTip">開啟角色選擇對話框。選一列以填入該 CharacterKey 值到文字框；按 Apply 寫入。</sys:String>

